attribs.current: The veteran makes two longsword attacks. If it has a shortsword drawn, it can also make a shortsword attack.

attribs.name: repeating_traits_-MkweHJuDSKHa611GT-g_description
attribs.current: You can move twice the normal amount of time (up to 16 hours) each day before being subject to the effect of a forced march (see “Travel Pace” in chapter 8 of the Player’s Handbook). Additionally, you can automatically find a safe route to land a boat on shore, provided such a route exists.
